<D>__{especially not then. i humiliated myself once.}
<A>__{now it's a row.}
<C>__{oblonsky}
<D>__{damn you, kostya, you love kitty and you can't forgive her because, first, you funked it, then you bungled it, then you ran away from an eighteen year old girl who was made a fool of by a uniform. it's kitty i'm sorry for not you!}
<C>__{levin}
<D>__{her heart told her no. did you come to shoot snipe or criticize me?}
